{"tid":2064710,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"西環集中營： 美或金融制裁中港 建制不知驚 - 季陶","createTime":"2020-06-15T04:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T07:14:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"22488d1177cfea549620323d3b205c89a713e342","tid":2064710,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:06:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200615/V5V46KFESBI2PAIKULBG3FHQYE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200615%2FV5V46KFESBI2PAIKULBG3FHQYE%2F&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8pgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=70989d45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200615%2FV5V46KFESBI2PAIKULBG3FHQYE%2F&h=e5ad0f9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200615/V5V46KFESBI2PAIKULBG3FHQYE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n西環集中營：<br />\n美或金融制裁中港 建制不知驚 - 季陶<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FGCGGESB6X23AZFI4ZWFXPK52E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFGCGGESB6X23AZFI4ZWFXPK52E.jpg&h=f4f41538&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然本周舉行的人大常委會議未有將港版國安法放入議程，但美國對制裁中、。。。。。。。。。。。。。。們仍堅信「美國唔會因為香港損害商界利益」，認為美不會有重手制裁。<br />\n<br />\n該金融界人士指，近日他與一些親北京商界及建制人士談港版國安法，當他一提到有關法例損中、港經濟及金融，他們即提醒要以「國家高度、國家安全層次去睇，唔好下下只睇經濟利益」；他一提到美國制裁，對方又以「美國商界喺香港有重大經濟利益，美國政府唔會犧牲利益重手制裁香港」，但當他反問，為何美國政府不會與北京一樣，從「國家高度」考慮，不顧經濟利益出手制裁？那些親北京商界及建制人士大多無法回答。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，即使是政府官員，他們回應美國。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。冇方法應對，到時對香港金融會造成無法想像打擊」。<br />\n<br />\n季陶<br />\n周一、三、五刊出"},{"pid":"5390ab59f7a5a0610707961c450e3efab2d57df8","tid":2064710,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T05:12:18.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47623c4663818eb9cf38da28e03a434a11f10bb6","tid":2064710,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:14:11.000Z","msg":"邱騰華，劏房波說話應該係佢地同中共真心話，認為美國唔會月用七傷拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}